data.description: Enjoy country living in this charming home located in the city on multiple parcels of .99 acres! This gem sits on multiple parcels, perfect to view the evening sunsets from the porch. This two-story home boasts 2 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, the second bedroom & bathroom are located upstairs overlooking the living area below. A nice retreat ready to call your own, schedule your showing today!
